<s> Labor Secretary Elizabeth Dole named a mediator to help resolve the lengthy labor dispute between the United Mine Workers and Pittston Co . </s>
<s> W.J. Usery Jr. , labor secretary during the Ford administration , was named to mediate talks to settle the six-month strike by the UMW . </s>
<s> Previous talks between Pittston , of Greenwich , Conn. , and the union have been sporadic and unsuccessful . </s>
<s> The union called the strike in April after Pittston refused to sign the UMW 's national labor pact . </s>
<s> Pittston seeks changes in health and pension benefits , among other things . </s>
<s> No schedule for formal talks was set , but meetings are expected to begin soon . </s>
